| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0298 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cd5f80c4-96e4-51e7-98f8-f5f1367fa228"
